def_en: If you head off a person, animal, or vehicle, you move to a place in front of them in order to capture them or make them change the direction they are moving in.

def_cn: 阻止，防止（尤指不愉快的事）发生
def_en: If you head something off, especially something unpleasant, you take action before it is expected to happen in order to prevent it from happening.
